<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<!-- FR3 URDF with F_T_EE appended by positronic-franka.
     Used as default for real hardware datasets that don't have robot_meta stored natively.
     Generated from: Robot('172.168.0.2').get_robot_model() on 2026-03-16.

     Visual meshes added by positronic for 3D visualization in the dataset server.
     The <visual> elements reference STL filenames (e.g. "link0.stl") that match files in
     positronic/assets/fr3_collision/. These are Panda collision meshes from robosuite
     (franka_description package) — FR3 shares the same link geometry as Panda.
     Added via: xml.etree.ElementTree, iterating links and adding <visual><geometry><mesh>
     for each link with a matching .stl file in the assets directory. -->
