  <!-- WARNING: This link and joint were appended by positronic-franka,
       NOT part of the original URDF from libfranka getRobotModel().
       They encode F_T_EE (flange-to-end-effector transform) read from
       franka::RobotState at the time of this call, so that the URDF
       matches the full kinematic chain used by the driver's runtime IK. -->
